The '''2017 Red Rooster Sydney SuperSprint''' was a [[auto racing|motor racing]] event for the [[Supercars Championship]], held on the weekend of 18 to 20 August 2017. The event was held at [[Sydney Motorsport Park]] in [[Eastern Creek, New South Wales|Eastern Creek]], [[New South Wales]] and consisted of two races, 120 and 200 kilometres in length. It is the ninth event of fourteen in the [[2017 Supercars Championship]] and hosted Races 17 and 18 of the season.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.supercars.com/2017-red-rooster-sydney-supersprint-schedule-results/|title=2017 Red Rooster Sydney SuperSprint Schedule & Results |website=Supercars.com|accessdate=11 December 2017}}</ref>
