'''Aya Ben Abdallah''' (born 19 August 1997) is a Tunisian [[handball]] player for [[Club Africain (handball)|Club Africain]] and the [[Tunisia women's national handball team|Tunisian national team]].

She participated at the [[2017 World Women's Handball Championship]].<ref>[http://www.ihf.info/files/CompetitionData/b7fe36bb-2a18-4340-a6e0-6b148a154448/pdf/TUN.pdf 2017 World Championship roster]</ref>

