'''Vancho Dimovski''' (born 4 April 1979) is a former Macedonian [[Team handball|handball]] player and former member of the [[Macedonia national handball team|Macedonian national team]]. In 2015 he became a sports director for [[RK Rabotnički]], but in February 2016 he left Rabotnički and became a team-manager at [[RK Metalurg Skopje]].
